Client Application Privacy Policy
Welcome to use our services (hereinafter referred to as "we", "our"). We are fully aware of your concern for personal privacy, and therefore promise to respect and protect the privacy rights of all users who use this application service (hereinafter referred to as the "Service"). The following privacy policy is designed to help you understand how we collect, use, store and share your information and how we protect your privacy.
1. Information collection:
When you use our services, we may collect the following types of information:
- Personal information: such as email address, phone number and other information you voluntarily provide.
- Device information: We may collect information about the device you use, including device model, operating system version, device settings, file and software names and types, etc.
- Log information: When you use our services or view content provided by us, we may automatically collect and store certain information in server logs. This includes, but is not limited to, IP address, browser type, browser language, date and time of access, and cookie information.
- Location information: When you turn on the device positioning function and use our related services, we may collect and process information about your actual location.
2. Use of information
We may use the information collected for the following purposes:
- Provide, maintain, protect and improve our services;
- Develop new services;
- To protect us and our users;
- Send you service updates, security warnings and support messages;
- Provide advertising and content that is more relevant to you.
3.Information sharing
Except for the following circumstances, we will not share your personal information with any third party without your consent:
- As required by law or to comply with judicial process;
- In the event of a merger, sale of assets, or other corporate transaction, if user information is transferred, we will require the new entity to comply with this Privacy Policy;
- To respond to fraud, security or technical issues;
- Share data for analytical or research purposes if anonymized or de-identified.
4.Information security
We are committed to protecting the security of our users' personal information. We have a variety of security measures in place to protect your information from loss, improper use, unauthorized access or disclosure. This includes the use of encryption technology during data transmission and the use of physical and electronic means to protect users’ personal information when stored.
5. User rights
You have the right to access, correct, delete your personal information, and also have the right to restrict or object to our processing of your information under certain circumstances. If you have any questions or concerns about your personal information or would like to exercise your rights, please contact us.
6.Children’s Privacy
Our services are not directed to children under 13 years of age. If we discover that personal information has been inadvertently collected from a child under 13, we will take steps to delete that information.
7. Privacy Policy Changes
We may update our privacy policy from time to time. We encourage users to periodically check this page for updates to our privacy policy. We will post any changes to our Privacy Policy on this page and, if the changes are material, we will provide a more prominent notice (including, for some services, an email notification of the privacy policy change).
8. "Apple Refund Processing and Personal Info Handling Guidelines:
To facilitate your refund request, you authorize Apple to gather key personal data necessary for review. This includes your Apple ID, purchase records, account activity logs, subscription details, partial payment info, refund reasons, and device specifics. 
This information is used solely for refund review and complies with privacy protection measures. By submitting your request, you agree to these terms. Thank you for your continued support!"
9.Contact us
If you have any questions about our privacy policy, please contact us at:
Email: hsliu@autheny.com
By using our Services, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy. We appreciate your concern for privacy and are committed to providing you with a safe, trustworthy service.
Thank you for using our App!